    "Foremost, the entities identified by CarD-T are potential candidates for carcinogenicity, not confirmed carcinogens.",
    "Additional processing, either through manual review or more sophisticated AI-based tools, is necessary to validate these findings.",
    "Furthermore, our current analysis is limited to abstracts, which may not capture the full nuances of study methods, result quality, or contextual details present in full-text articles.",
